<bibRefCitation author="Curletti" box="[664,908,2000,2023]" pageId="0" pageNumber="373" refString="Curletti, G. &amp; Brule, S. (2011) Agrilus, Agriloides et Autarcontes de Guyane. Ex Natura, Magellanes, 2, 1 - 84." type="journal article" year="2011">Curletti &amp; Brûlé 2011</bibRefCitation>
